---
title: Cal Smart Mojo-Inspired Turkey with Spinach-Citrus Salad
description: Got a touch of the winter blues? Take a tropical trip with this calorie friendly turkey salad. Jerk seasoning, garlic and citrus juice all bring the flavour of the Caribbean without ever leaving the comfort of your home!

Calorie Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie amount.
